r3094 | ajc | 2004-06-01 02:36:43 +0200 (Tue, 01 Jun 2004) | 3 lines

* Hmmph.  Do the session cookie as hex instead of base64.  There really
  are some characters in the base64 set that make HTTP do nasty things.

